data.description:
!! Sellers will contribute 1% of purchase price (at closing) towards buyer's closing costs or interest rate buy down !!

Wonderful Silver Creek home in Clay County, Built in 2005. With a brand new roof in 2020! 
This is 1800 sq ft that feels much bigger in person!

Community Pool and other facilities! NO CDD!

Split floorplan features 3 bed/2 Bath + formal dining and a flex room/office space that could be easily enclosed or converted to a 4th bedroom. 

Large, tiled kitchen with breakfast nook. Stainless steel appliances included as well as island, and bar.

 LVP flooring throughout the dining room, family room, office/flex room, & guest bath. 

Owner's bath boasts dual sinks, built in vanity, walk-in closet, garden tub & separate tiled shower.

Main appliances included!
